snippet.title: X-Treme Quads (PS2 Gameplay)
snippet.description:
X-Treme Quads (PS2) - Quad Bike: Tiger - Stage: Outlaw Canyon Stage 1

Start your engines! X-Treme Quads features wild quad bike racing over even wilder terrain. So, hold on tight!
There are miles and miles of unrelenting track to cover before you can be crowned the champion, and the only guarantee is that the ride is going to be X-Treme!
